<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١١٨٩ - <span class="c2">(خ)</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4563">عَلِيٌّ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">الزُّهْرِيِّ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2436">سَعِيدٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>،<span class="c5"> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا تُشَدُّ الرِّحَالُ إِلَّا إِلَى ثَلَاثَةِ مَسَاجِدَ؛ الْمَسْجِدِ الْحَرَامِ، وَمَسْجِدِ الرَّسُولِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>، وَمَسْجِدِ الْأَقْصَى»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>